RELEASE NOTES
=============

This is the release "1.8.0" of the BANDIT toolkit.
This is a "STABLE" release.

See https://docs.phyglos.org/bandit for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES
=============

*  Check whether some item is used in a bundle command
*  Allow --tag parameter in bundles
*  Refactored RELEASE_TAG variables
*  Added bandit_show_bandit() function


